{"tid":32290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女模堅持不睡土豪　純約會換免費環遊世界","createTime":"2016-12-10T06:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T12:32:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2854cda7b9bdd9c7e5526ced496016289f3f6126","tid":32290,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:02:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o8zQnEax2Ao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do8zQnEax2Ao&d=zPe0sGypNpw8mTORrJqLm0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=6d0134d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o8zQnEax2Ao</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161210/640_011eea15d27dfa9601413810299f6121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161210%2F640_011eea15d27dfa9601413810299f6121.jpg&h=8b8d3a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國一名20歲內衣女模拉莫絲(Alyssa Ramos)，她的夢想就是環遊世界，而她堅持不睡土豪，透過網路找到資助者約會，讓她得以免費環遊世界。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161210/420_7b63cd5ecd52bf773bb1a5750d7b3d2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161210%2F420_7b63cd5ecd52bf773bb1a5750d7b3d2b.jpg&h=b4a30007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日星報》報導，拉莫絲透過「Miss Travel」網站平台，認識許多願意資助她的網友，她號稱已經去過倫敦、紐約、伊維薩島以及杜拜等地，而且所有的食宿費、機票錢通通是「免費」。拉莫絲說，她和願意資助她的網友們見面，一起約會吃飯，「每一個我所見過的男網友，都會為我付錢，只要我想出錢，他們都會說『不用』，真的好紳士喔」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161210/420_d4331fe2dc782d2e5c3ba570c7187b61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161210%2F420_d4331fe2dc782d2e5c3ba570c7187b61.jpg&h=ae65d532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拉莫絲也強調，她和約會者都是純約會，只有親吻、抱抱、聊聊天而已，絕對沒有上床睡覺。她也說，她對老男人比較有興趣，先前交往過一名48歲的中年男子，但交往2年後分手，也開啟她環遊世界之路。現在她正計畫從巴哈馬玩到希臘，而她至今也已經與5名男子約會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.travelpulse.com/images/99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999/d94be4b6-b7bb-e511-8b9f-0050568e420d/630x355.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.travelpulse.com%2Fimages%2F99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999%2Fd94be4b6-b7bb-e511-8b9f-0050568e420d%2F630x355.jpg&h=fc5f30e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"745eb2079607081b28111c51acf2be75d8b90046","tid":32290,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:04:13.000Z","msg":"雞......仲要好自豪果隻"},{"pid":"1a53368f430b3ac80280442f44bbb2c355aa2db2","tid":32290,"uid":16283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:12:28.000Z","msg":"41j"},{"pid":"c779f2168480001650e7588f3e7b2655ee226dfb","tid":32290,"uid":53261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:15:02.000Z","msg":"她和約會者都是純約會，只有親吻、抱抱、聊聊天而已，絕對沒有上床睡覺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb3ffc695177b1ed23667d6e99db86fca173eca","tid":32290,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:19:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>她和約會者都是純約會，只有<span style=\"color: red;\">親吻</span>、抱抱、聊聊天而已，絕對沒有上床睡覺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無sex plan既貴價ptgf"},{"pid":"2d4feba8e6bcc03ec113602911ba5935331d8b28","tid":32290,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:23:06.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"e35c70accda370ce548937e603e015f3a33c4c00","tid":32290,"uid":55113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:24:58.000Z","msg":"對鬼妹黎講kiss跟本唔算得係咩"},{"pid":"0dd4d25904e7e2c99e1badb9af11c5987521a54e","tid":32290,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:25:36.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"e17575496cce8b2caaaed54d31cf78e0e2d0924c","tid":32290,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:27:34.000Z",